title: How I take Notes (College) using my iPad Pro!
description:
I hope you found this video helpful! If you're new to my channel... please subscribe to join my family...I'd be happy to have you! XOXO -Ky

Application Used: Microsoft One Note
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/microsoft-onenote/id784801555?mt=12

iPad Pro 9.7 inch 
Silver
128 gb

I chose the 9.7 inch, because I felt as though it was more comfortable in the hand. The 12 inch was rather large. I feel like if I'm going carry around a device thats 12 inches I might at well just grab my Mac.

Belkin Apple Pencil Case and Stand:
http://www.target.com/p/belkin-apple-pencil-case-and-stand/-/A-51674499
